channel.title: Paradise 317 [Allstar]
channel.description: [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/dhaj46.png[/img] Reason I Chose Allstar: Many people, like myself, enjoy Allstar, Due to the fact Players could have a fun time. Me and 2 of my friends decided to create a Allstar server, with one purpose in mind: A Very Light economy, with a server revolving around the Players, All of our content is aimed to make the players experience More Entertaining, and Fun. Client Download: http://www.mediafire.com/?t98yui7y4ldstvr DOWNLOAD UPDATED CLIENT ABOVE, OR YOU WILL NOT BE ABLE TO CONNECT. Also Forums: [url=http://paradise317.proboards.com]paradise317.proboards.com[/url] Now, I will display some media we have taken. ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0003_zps3aeba004.png[/img] We have Pk point rewards, for those who love to Pk! [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0001_zpsdac1a2d3.png[/img] Our Bank Pin System, Created by Alex! [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0002_zps144a8cea.png[/img] 200m Gamble, To have a chance at a variety of items! [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0016_zps173fdcc2.png[/img] Classic Godsword Mini X.D. [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0007_zps879fe451.png[/img] Jad, With some changes. [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0004_zpse2e5c3d4.png[/img] Pkbox! [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0003_zps9a5e1681.png[/img] Funpk, items are not lost on death. [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0001_zps544c6869.png[/img] Veng + One of our training Zones! [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0006_zps224f3e87.png[/img] Barrows Brothers. [IMG]http://i1326.photobucket.com/albums/u654/Dokan42/evolved0011_zps8d413cc3.png[/img] Skilling Zone, Train skills here. X.D. Other things not mentioned in the pictures: Anti-SYI Protection. Client Music, Add your own playlist, or listen to our 3 Songs that come with the client. Player Saving Works, Your player will save properly. Many Bosses Not Mentioned Within The Pictures. Some Custom Items, for those who enjoy that kind of thing. ::max to show max hit. Dark bow Minigame, and a minigame to get christmas crackers/cash. Kalphite queen to get some sexy decorative items. A 1v1 zone. Trade Dupe Fixed. Many Other Dupes Fixed. Glitch to go invisible fixed. Custom items have animations and stats. Yell Colors! Thanks To Alex! The server runs on a auto restarter, so updates can be applied if needed. A ::suggest command, we listen to player suggestions, unless they are completely 'Out there' Server Has a unused music tab, debating what to put there. Crappy Skillcape emotes, which you'd expect from a Allstar Server. Planning to change some of them. *Much more that I have not mentioned, Feel free to join us, and have a fun time* Clan chat system! A General Store To sell and buy items from! WE DO NOT, AND NEVER WILL ACCEPT DONATIONS, THIS SERVER IS MEANT FOR THE PLAYERS ENJOYMENT, NOT FOR MONEY.
